fde","tid":498430,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T19:18:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱左手唔夠一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分左手唔夠一個月</blockquote><br />\n巴打放低到未？<br />\n如果拖到臨聖誕先嚟分肯定會仲傷"},{"pid":"d3e67ee380e7d67afce0d3001076c5d42659c9f4","tid":498430,"uid":74088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T19:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實每年都係 有研究講過分手係有季節性</blockquote><br />\n願聞其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 唔啱嘅早分早著啦"},{"pid":"93de8c321fa590b4973005cc2c2438a9d8c20c62","tid":498430,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T19:21:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實每年都係 有研究講過分手係有季節性</blockquote><br />\n係咩原理？<br />\n唔係臨近聖誕先想拍拖咩"},{"pid":"911dde4fa3ee8f0501b41f0c66bb04d640afa104","tid":498430,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T19:31:35.000Z","msg":"舊年聖誕仲祝緊天下情人係失散兄妹，今年我都唔敢亂講嘢"},{"pid":"b2b7ebbdc9eda94c265ffd53ca1dc2e15fe05f2f","tid":498430,"uid":27793,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T19:37:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/033114_e9b01e00ac3abcfc9ecf6a425c41b3c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F033114_e9b01e00ac3abcfc9ecf6a425c41b3c4.jpg&h=17c78f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冬天多情侶分手 主兇季節性情緒失調？<br />\n<br />\n到冬天時，個人情緒相對地容易出事！有一種症狀叫「季節性情緒失調」（Seasonal Affective Disorder），又稱為「冬季憂鬱症」（Winter Depression）。根據美國奧勒岡健康與科學大學的精神病學教授Alfred Lewy指出，由於不少人面對新季節的轉變，適應能力會變得緩慢，大腦中的松果體在少陽光環境下會釋放褪黑素，而「季節性情緒失調」的病患在冬天時釋放的褪黑素比一般人高。<br />\n<br />\n冬天情侶易出事？<br />\n<br />\n而根據CNN網站曾報道過，英國作家David McCandless早前綜合大家在facebook公布status（感情狀況）的統計，情人節分手為榜首，其次就是聖誕前兩星期。另外有研究表示情侶們在冬天考慮分手的機會率，相比在其他時間考慮多出兩倍以上。有可能是因為情緒受到影響，人缺乏陽光的照射，體內減少吸收血清素，而血清素是一種神經傳導物質，負責傳遞訊息到神經細胞，所以導致我們容易變得情緒化，又會成日認為「你唔愛我啦」！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gotrip.hk/ladies_talk/%E5%AD%A3%E7%AF%80%E6%80%A7%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E5%A4%B1%E8%AA%BF-%E6%83%85%E4%BE%B6%E5%88%86%E6%89%8B/4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gotrip.hk%2Fladies_talk%2F%25E5%25AD%25A3%25E7%25AF%2580%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25B7%2592%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25AA%25BF-%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25BE%25B6%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%2589%258B%2F4%2F&d=Gxsk75OkkcuDYziVBr3lDtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=5cf3633f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gotrip.hk/ladies_talk/%E5%AD%A3%E7%AF%80%E6%80%A7%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E5%A4%B1%E8%AA%BF-%E6%83%85%E4%BE%B6%E5%88%86%E6%89%8B/4/</a>"},{"pid":"7c6c94f8d39d52b9c3b2baf8c21d4089f204ed48","tid":498430,"uid":76697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:34:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}